content.raw:
The `state.tlog` stores protobuf files from topics. The `proto` descriptions can be found [here](https://bitbucket.org/ignitionrobotics/ign-msgs/src/default/proto/ignition/msgs/).

The `state.tlog` itself is an sqlite3 file.
